          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "So that definitely added a fun element to the trip. But, Bern can be a great place to visit any time of the year, so without further ado, here is my guide for things to do and places to eat in Bern at any time of the year. I've also included our Airbnb as a suggestion for a place to stay in the city because we loved it!"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 1
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Places to Eat"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Einstein Kaffee"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Einstein Kaffee is a very cute and cozy restaurant and coffee house in the heart of Bern. We actually tried to eat here several times before succeeding. It was always packed when we went, which was a bit stressful, but we were finally able to grab a table the morning of Daniel's birthday. The food and coffee were great. Even though this place may seem a bit touristy, we felt like we were surrounded by locals and the quality of the food and coffee did not disappoint!"
          }
        ]
