      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For Valentine's Day dinner, we picked a restaurant with a view! The food was good, but the best part was the view of Bern's Old Town. Even if you don't want to splurge on a nice dinner, you should find your way up to the Rosengarten to get some photos. I wish we had had time to go back up during the daytime for a different experience and higher quality photos, but the view at night was stunning!"
          }
        ]
